TrapDoor - Class in com.mycompany.ui.staticShapes
The trapdoor class extends polygon as it is a static shape and it is a collidable When scanned square (scanned by the trapdoor scanner) has a trapdoor status of true it will allow the square to pass through, instead of going down the conveyor as it is technically a conveyor.
